  "text": "In the recent paper [CITATION_1] , a space discretization of the multicomponent Yajima-Oikawa system (1.2), where ∆ + n is the forward difference operator, i.e., ∆ + n f n := f n+1 − f n , was proposed using the Hirota bilinear method and multisoliton solutions in terms of pfaffians were constructed. We set 1 + 1 2 L n =: v n and consider a slightly generalized version of (1.3):",
